head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths WINCHESTER, MADELINE K.

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths WINCHESTER, MADELINE K.

block.p: WINCHESTER-Madeline K. On September 24, 2000 at age 91. Beloved wife of the late William Winchester, loving mother of Dr. Robert Winchester and grandmother of Alan and Priscilla Winchester. Friends may call at Frank E. Campbell, 1076 Madison Ave at 81 St Tuesday and Wednesday 2-5 and 7-9pm. Funeral Mass at St Monica's Church, 413 E 79 St, Thursday 10am. Interment to follow at Gate of Heavan Cemetery.
